and our divinity.

00:23:09.500 --> 00:23:10.650 align:middle line:90%
How do we integrate them?

00:23:10.650 --> 00:23:13.190 align:middle line:84%
How do we bring all
of the great things

00:23:13.190 --> 00:23:17.570 align:middle line:84%
we're doing for ourselves into
a practical, grounded way, day

00:23:17.570 --> 00:23:19.280 align:middle line:90%
by day, minute by minute?

